<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="56" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,1636,2010]" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">
The occurrence of this species in Brazil was cited by 
<bibRefCitation author="Grifo, F. T." box="[897,1056,1790,1816]" pageId="5" pageNumber="56" refId="ref6759" refString="Grifo, F. T. (1992) A revision of Myrcianthes Berg (Myrtaceae). Ph. D. thesis, Cornell University, Ithaca, 327 p." type="book" year="1992">Grifo (1992)</bibRefCitation>
, based on a MICH collection (
<emphasis box="[161,380,1829,1854]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">Hatschbach 22932</emphasis>
). We had the opportunity to examine 
<emphasis box="[819,1038,1829,1854]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">Hatschbach 22932</emphasis>
at MBM and, although it presents dichasial inflorescences reminding those of several species of 
<taxonomicName box="[932,1085,1868,1893]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcianthes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="5" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[932,1085,1868,1893]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">Myrcianthes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, the MBM sheet is in fact a collection of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Kunth) O. Berg. No" authorityName="O. Berg. No" baseAuthorityName="Kunth" box="[310,825,1906,1932]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Blepharocalyx" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="5" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="salicifolius">
<emphasis box="[310,623,1907,1932]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">Blepharocalyx salicifolius</emphasis>
(Kunth) O.Berg
</taxonomicName>
. No additional Brazilian collection of 
<taxonomicName class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" genus="Myrcianthes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="5" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pseudomato">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="56">Myrcianthes pseudomato</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was examined since this citation; so, we have not included this species in the final list of Brazilian 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Berg" authorityYear="1857" box="[266,393,1984,2010]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Myrtaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Myrtales" pageId="5" pageNumber="56" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Myrtaceae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
